import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper } from '@mui/material'; import { toWords } from 'number-to-words'; const FormComponentMPT2 = ({ rollNumber, name, sod, examDate, subjectsData, specialty }) => { const [grandTotal, setGrandTotal] = useState(0); const [totalInWords, setTotalInWords] = useState(''); useEffect(() => { const total = subjectsData.reduce((acc, subj) => acc + (subj.totalSecured || 0), 0); setGrandTotal(total); setTotalInWords(toWords(total).toUpperCase()); }, [subjectsData]); return ( MEMORANDUM OF MARKS Roll No: {rollNumber} MASTER OF PHYSIOTHERAPY
2nd Year Final Examination held in {examDate} Specialty: {specialty} Name: {name} D/o.S/o.: {sod} Paper No. Subject Theory Practical / Viva Total Marks Secured Result Max Min. Sec. Max Min. Sec. (Theory + Practical/Viva) {subjectsData.map((subj, index) => ( {subj.paperNo} {subj.subject} {subj.theoryMax} {subj.theoryMin} {subj.theorySecured} {subj.practicalMax} {subj.practicalMin} {subj.practicalMax === 'NA' ? 'NA' : subj.practicalSecured} {subj.totalSecured} {subj.result} ))} *': { fontWeight: 'bold' } }}> Total {grandTotal}
Aggregate marks (in words): {totalInWords} Result: PASS ); }; export default FormComponentMPT2;
